[]: Rei/Kaworu connection &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Quote Post by Staffy3 &raquo; Mon Nov 29, 2010 4:18 pm Ok, we all know that Kaworu and Rei have red eyes and are perceived by viewers to be the Adam and Lilith of the &quot;modern age.&quot; Well, what about the way Kaworu addresses Rei in the Director&#39;s cut of episode 24? &quot;We are the same.&quot; Certainly it could be dismissed that they are similar in that they are the reincarnarion of Adam/Lilith, Angels etc. but what about their Surnames? Nagisa and Ayanami. Not only do the words refer to Sea and Shore, a reference to the ending of EoE, but also Izanami and Izanagi are the Adam of Lilith of the Shinto religion. I thought this to be interesting considering the majority of references are related with Christianity and Judaism. I&#39;m sorry if this or anything similar has been posted before. I&#39;d love to hear your opinions on this. :&#41;

